{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"be1ac41aa0","title":"菜裕部可南下破路弃故","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"16330782c1","index":0,"year":1947,"month":12,"day":20,"articleId":"be1ac41aa0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ff1f283365","type":"paragraph","text":"菜裕部可南下破路弃故”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"be1ac41aa0"},{"id":"11dfc3d4fc","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年12月20日）采，并告陈、谢项接陈谢二十日十四时电，主张你部四个纵队南下，打现到明港附近正北向新安店进之整三师（两个旅），然后向信阳前进。如你们同意向南，即可部署行动。似此，你们应不为从前划定之界线所束纯，而向整个平汉路及其两侧机动，以破坏平汉路及歼灭敌若千个旅为目标（希望能牙敌五六个旅）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"be1ac41aa0"},{"id":"0452f057c5","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"be1ac41aa0"},{"id":"798fd72f5f","type":"paragraph","text":"二十日二十四时H这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华东野战军副简令员票裕的电报。2]陈、谢，指陈座、谢富治，当时分别任晋冀鲁豫野战军陈谢集团前委书记和副书记。[3]平汉路，指北平（今北京）至汉口的铁路，即今京广线一段。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"be1ac41aa0"}],"page":{"id":"d96e4697d9","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"be1ac41aa0","start":429,"end":429}}}},"__N_SSG":true}